我那样做是因为我喜欢
Things I do, I do them because
I like them.

1444
01:55:35,080 --> 01:55:36,640
因为我想做
Because I want to.

1445
01:56:24,600 --> 01:56:26,960
你被刀伤，多少刀？
You've been stabbed? How many times?

1446
01:56:27,120 --> 01:56:29,520
先生，请问你叫什么名字？
Sir, can you tell me your name?

1447
01:57:20,840 --> 01:57:22,160
是你吗？
Is that you?

1448
01:57:25,840 --> 01:57:27,000
我的天
My God.

1449
01:57:45,040 --> 01:57:46,360
救我
Save me.

1450
01:57:51,680 --> 01:57:53,200
救我
Save me.

1451
01:59:06,280 --> 01:59:07,280
谢谢

1452
01:59:09,360 --> 01:59:11,000
亲爱的魏斯先生:
Dear Mr. Welles:

1453
01:59:11,280 --> 01:59:12,600
谢谢你的来信
Thank you for writing...

1454
01:59:12,840 --> 01:59:15,040
并告诉我你的真名字
...and telling me your real name...

1455
01:59:15,280 --> 01:59:18,040
你的真正身份和真正发生的事
...who you really are
and what really happened.

1456
01:59:18,280 --> 01:59:20,600
我很高兴那些人都死了
I'm glad those men are dead.

1457
01:59:20,960 --> 01:59:24,120
但我心灵的伤口却永远
不会被填平
But nothing will ever
fill the hole in my heart.

1458
01:59:24,280 --> 01:59:27,280
我会将你寄给我的钱做点好事
I will try to use
the money you sent for some good...

1459
01:59:27,520 --> 01:59:29,960
但会在我替自己疗伤之后
...after I  get some help for myself.

1460
01:59:30,200 --> 01:59:32,440
我恨你将事实告诉我
I  hated you
for telling me the truth...

1461
01:59:32,600 --> 01:59:36,200
但我感觉到你和我可能是
...but now I  realize you and I 
are probably the only people...

1462
01:59:36,440 --> 01:59:38,960
这世上唯一关心玛丽 安的人
...that ever really
cared about Mary Anne.

1463
01:59:39,120 --> 01:59:40,800
珍纳麦修
Yours truly...

1464
01:59:41,120 --> 01:59:42,640
上
...Janet Mathews.

1465
02:00:06,240 --> 02:00:08,720
～剧终～

1466
02:00:09,720 --> 02:00:12,760
～谢谢观赏～

